  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetDeviceType</TypeRef> method returns the type of the graphics device, as defined by the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.DeviceType">DeviceType</PageRef>
      enumeration.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[DeviceType GetDeviceType() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="DeviceType!cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.DeviceType">
        The type of this device
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
